# Guardrails — {{BRAND_NAME}}

Learned constraints + failure patterns.
Update this file every time you hit a new issue — so the next session doesn't repeat it.

## Image
- NEVER hotlink to external CDN URLs in production
- NEVER use image > 500KB without optimization
- ALWAYS provide descriptive alt text (not "image" or "photo")
- WebP + JPEG fallback for all production images

## Audio / Video
- NEVER auto-play without user interaction
- ALWAYS provide accessible pause button (≥44px tap)
- ALWAYS reserve space before media loads (no CLS)
- ALWAYS check `prefers-reduced-motion` before playing animation

## Form
- NEVER submit without server-side validation
- NEVER trust client-side validation alone
- ALWAYS use a proper `<form>` element with submit handler — not `<div>` + onClick
  (Without this: Enter key broken, autofill broken, screen reader can't identify as form)
- ALWAYS show errors inline, not alert()
- Include honeypot field for bot protection

## Design Tokens
- NEVER hardcode hex values in components or templates
- NEVER use arbitrary spacing values outside the defined scale
- All colors and spacing MUST reference CSS custom properties from tokens.css
- Run `pnpm check:tokens` before committing

## Accessibility
- NEVER skip `prefers-reduced-motion` check for video/animation
- NEVER use color as the only indicator (add icon/text)
- `<nav>` MUST have `aria-label` if more than one nav exists on the page
- All tap/click targets MUST be ≥44px (WCAG 2.1 SC 2.5.5)
- ALWAYS provide focus-visible state

## SVG
- SVG `<text>` elements can fail silently when processed by image optimizers
  Fix: serve SVGs as static files or use `unoptimized` flags in framework image components
- Avoid relying on system fonts in SVG — use paths or web fonts

## Performance
- NEVER load heavy libraries (audio players, charts) at page load — lazy load on scroll/interaction
- NEVER skip font preloading (causes FOUT/FOIT)
- ALWAYS test on slow 3G before shipping

## Claude Code Skills
- Skills MUST be at `.claude/skills/{name}/SKILL.md` with YAML frontmatter
- `.agents/skills/` path does NOT work — Claude Code ignores it entirely

